      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it's time for a new home! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014I've babied it since day one, and it truly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
