    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive specimen of Bavarian high-performance engineering. The S54B32 inline-six remains the centerpiece, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a flawlessly calibrated Double VANOS system. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and a full overhaul of the cooling system, ensuring thermal efficiency under load. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential with factory-spec lockup. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by Bilstein coilover dampening, while the exterior retains its original luster, free of oxidation or panel misalignment. Every bushing, seal, and gasket has been inspected to meet concours standards, making this a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
