    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved by a single owner and kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its accident-free history. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of creasing or wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. All electronic systems, including the premium audio and navigation, operate with factory precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is indistinguishable from new, with a complete service portfolio documented exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen that offers a 'new car' experience at a significant value. Inspection will satisfy even the most discerning buyer.",
